        <item>
            <title>Apple 推出 iOS 17.4　3 个重点功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios-17-4-3-new-feature</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:52:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iOS 17.4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[carplay]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222508</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 日前发布了 iOS 17.4 正式版，是次更新主要是为了符合欧盟《数码市场法案》（Digintal Markets Act，DMA），另外亦更新了 CarPlay、在 Apple Podcast 加入了逐字稿（Transcript），同时亦新增不少 Emoji。现在就让小编和大家分享一下这次 iOS 17.4 有甚么更新重点吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222753" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709702878.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><h2>1. 6 个新 Emoij + 人物表情符号可向左向右</h2><p>iOS 17.4 加入了 6 个全新 Emoji，包括蘑菇、凤凰、断掉的锁链、点头及摇头 Emoji。另外是次更新亦为用户提供更多 Emoji 选项，其中有 18 款有关人物和身体的 Emoji 提供另一方向，让用家可以自由选择 Emoji 面向左边抑或右边。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781-476x580.jpeg" alt="" width="476" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781-476x580.jpeg 476w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028781.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 476px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点头、摇头 Emoji</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783-475x580.jpeg" alt="" width="475" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783-475x580.jpeg 475w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028783.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲蘑菇、青柠 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg" alt="" width="480" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 480px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲凤凰、断掉的锁链 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg" alt="" width="480" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782-480x580.jpeg 480w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097028782.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 480px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲凤凰、断掉的锁链 Emoji</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260-521x580.jpeg" alt="" width="521" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260-521x580.jpeg 521w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709703260.jpeg 808w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 521px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现在用家可以自由选择部分 Emoji 面向的方向</p><h2>2. Apple Podcasts 加入逐字稿 </h2><p>iOS 17.4 更新后， Apple Podcast 加入了 Transcript（逐字稿）功能，运作原理类似 Apple Music 的歌词般，让用家能够随 Podcast 的进度，以文字形式阅读 Podcast 的内容。目前这个功能支援英文、西班牙文、法文及德文。除了可以跟随 Podcast 进度同步显示逐字稿外，用家亦可一次过阅读整篇文稿，以及搜寻特定字眼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo1709705270.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple Podcast 现时可提供逐字稿</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701-267x580.jpeg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701-267x580.jpeg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/photo17097052701.jpeg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家亦可搜寻特定字眼</p><p>Apple 表示，用家更新 iOS 17.4 后就可立即开始使用新 Podcast 功能，暂时不会提供转译功能，意思是如果 Podcast 本身是以英文录制的话，Apple Podcast 暂时仅会提供英文逐字稿。</p><h2>3. CarPlay 能在仪表板显示 Apple 地图资料</h2><p>iOS 17.4 之前，Apple Car Play 仅能在主萤幕显示 Apple Map 街道方向，仪表板则显示导航路线概览。现在如果驾驶者仪表板配备显示器的话，可以与主显示器交替切换显示街道视图和路线视图。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222768" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/carplay174.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2024/02/carplay-17.4.webp?resize=1536,768">9to5Mac</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/03/apple-introduces-transcripts-for-apple-podcasts">Apple</a>、<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/03/05/ios-17-4-now-available/">9to5Mac</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/apple-ios-174-can-sideload/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple iOS 17.4 九大更新重点【懒人包】开放侧载、第三方可用 NFC 支付</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-3/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.4 将有第三方应用商店　开发者无需向苹果支付额外费用</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/ios-17-4-3-new-feature/software/ios-app/">Apple 推出 iOS 17.4　3 个重点功能</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
